        p If you didn't request this password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.
        
        p For security reasons, this link will expire in 1 hour. If you need to reset your password after it expires, please submit a new request.
        
        p If you have any questions or need further assistance, please contact our support team at #{supportEmail}.
        
        p Best regards,
        br
        | The HAWO Salon Team
      
